text: Coos Bay is a bay on the coast of Oregon in the United States. Coos Bay may also refer to: * Coos Bay, Oregon, a city in Oregon ** Port of Coos Bay ** Coos Bay Rail Link * , a United States Navy seaplane tender in commission from 1943 to 1946 * , later WHEC-376, a United States Coast Guard cutter in commission from 1949 to 1966 ==See also== * Coos (disambiguation)
